{"tid":785030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人知經銅鑼灣番官塘架紅van係咪無咗","createTime":"2018-08-18T21:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T03:35:48.000Z","uid":119027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3cb5cc7592de4db0d9486c60fa84c77fbd6cf4","tid":785030,"uid":119027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T21:10:49.000Z","msg":"話說我係番夜更<br />\n每日大概四點幾收<br />\n以前會行去鵝頸橋底搭紅van<br />\n點知佢上個月開始尾班變左三點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算數我行遠啲喺南洋酒店等另一架都係去觀塘<br />\n但係呢幾日都唔見左架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等極都無<br />\n請問除左轉工仲可以點樣快啲番到屋企"},{"pid":"1b6b4aeeaae00ef8821cb4e6d1801dfaeb6c18f4","tid":785030,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T21:12:37.000Z","msg":"N619"},{"pid":"3038d847757c9e9cc3604e4be25dd2b21f336cef","tid":785030,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"的士"}]}